    ApplicationBusinessException

    ApplicationException

    ApplicationTechnicalException

    IllegalEntityStateException
    This exception is thrown if an entity has a specific state that is illegal for the current operation and caused it to fail.
    IllegalPropertyChangeException
    This exception is thrown if an entity has a specific state that is illegal for the current operation and caused it to fail.
    NoActiveUserException
    Thrown when an operation is requested that requires a user to be logged in, but no such user exists.
